---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="List Your Practice | For Psychologists | Sydney Anxiety Psychology Directory"
  description="List your telehealth psychology practice on the Sydney Anxiety Psychology directory. Free profile, inbound patient enquiries, a do-follow backlink to your practice, and a Founding Practitioner badge. Takes two minutes."
>
  <div class="main-content">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 700px;">

      <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <a href="/">Home</a> &rsaquo; For Psychologists
      </p>

      <!-- Hero -->
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent-soft), var(--color-warm)); border: 1px solid var(--color-accent-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2.5rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
        <p style="display: inline-block; font-size: 0.74rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent-hover); background: var(--color-accent-light); border: 1px solid rgba(21,116,105,0.2); padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Founding Practitioner Spots Available</p>
        <h1 style="font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); margin-bottom: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.15;">Your profile is already here. Claim it free.</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; max-width: 580px;">Sydney Anxiety Psychology is a directory that connects patients seeking telehealth psychology with AHPRA-registered practitioners. We have pre-built profiles from the AHPRA public register. Claim yours in two minutes and start receiving inbound enquiries at no cost.</p>
        <a href="#apply" class="btn btn--primary" style="font-size: 1rem;">
          Claim or apply for a free listing
        </a>
        <p style="font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-top: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 0;">No referral fee. No subscription. Nothing to pay.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Value stack -->
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">What you get</h2>
      <div style="display: grid; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">

        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1.1rem; align-items: flex-start; background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.4rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);">
          <span style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 44px; height: 44px; background: var(--color-accent-soft); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/></svg>
          </span>
          <div>
            <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">A profile that ranks on Google</strong>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.94rem;">Your listing is optimised for searches like "telehealth psychologist anxiety Sydney" and "[your name] psychologist." For practitioners without their own site, this is often the fastest path to a Google presence. For those with a website, it is a second result and a trust signal.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1.1rem; align-items: flex-start; background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.4rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);">
          <span style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 44px; height: 44px; background: var(--color-accent-soft); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </span>
          <div>
            <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">Inbound patient enquiries, no referral fee</strong>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.94rem;">When a patient submits our "connect me with a psychologist" form, we match their needs to suitable practitioners in our directory and pass the enquiry to you directly. No commission. No referral fee. Patients looking for telehealth psychology for anxiety are specifically what this directory attracts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1.1rem; align-items: flex-start; background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.4rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);">
          <span style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 44px; height: 44px; background: var(--color-accent-soft); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
          </span>
          <div>
            <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">Founding Practitioner badge (limited)</strong>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.94rem;">The first practitioners to claim a listing receive a permanent "Founding Practitioner" badge on their profile. This signals early adoption of a growing directory and, for prospective patients, a level of engagement with the telehealth model. Once the founding cohort is full, this badge is no longer available.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1.1rem; align-items: flex-start; background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.4rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);">
          <span style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 44px; height: 44px; background: var(--color-accent-soft); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/></svg>
          </span>
          <div>
            <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">Do-follow backlink to your practice</strong>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.94rem;">Your profile includes a do-follow link to your booking page or practice website. This is a genuine SEO benefit: links from topically relevant, indexed health directories are meaningful signals. If you do not have a website yet, we list your preferred contact method instead.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1.1rem; align-items: flex-start; background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.4rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);">
          <span style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 44px; height: 44px; background: var(--color-accent-soft); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <div>
            <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">Free guest article byline (optional)</strong>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.94rem;">You can submit one short article (500 to 800 words) on your area of clinical expertise, published under your name on this site with a link back to your profile. Good for credibility, SEO, and demonstrating expertise to prospective patients. Not required; entirely optional.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Who this is for -->
      <div class="info-box" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <p><strong>Who this is for:</strong> AHPRA-registered psychologists (registered or endorsed clinical) who are based in or serve Greater Sydney, offer or are open to telehealth appointments, and have experience with anxiety presentations (GAD, panic disorder, social anxiety, health anxiety, OCD, or similar). If you are a psychologist in a related area who wants to discuss fit, the notes field is the right place.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- How it works -->
      <h2>How it works</h2>
      <ol class="steps" style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
        <li>
          <div>
            <strong>Submit the form below</strong>
            <p>It takes about two minutes. If your profile is already pre-built from the AHPRA register, it is waiting for you to claim. If not, we will create it.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div>
            <strong>We review and publish your listing</strong>
            <p>We verify your AHPRA registration, add your specialties, booking link, and bio, and publish your profile within 2 business days. AHPRA compliance is checked before any profile goes live.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div>
            <strong>You start receiving enquiries</strong>
            <p>Patient enquiries that match your profile are forwarded to the email you provide. You decide whether to proceed with each enquiry. There is no obligation to accept every referral.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <!-- Form -->
      <div id="apply">
        <h2>Apply for a free listing</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Fill in the details below and we will be in touch within 2 business days. Fields marked * are required.</p>

        <form
          method="POST"
          action="https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbxlGPGS_ZjNlbF0uBl_WC0yp3-J6TSl_DYiYqUIjxcitQyCDKDO60E0gOSxFfxwZmQz/exec"
          style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 2rem;"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="_form" value="listing" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_site" value="anxiety-sydney" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://sydneyanxietypsychology.com.au/for-psychologists/thank-you/" />
          <input type="text" name="_gotcha" style="display: none;" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />

          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
            <div>
              <label for="psych-name" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">Full name *</label>
              <input type="text" id="psych-name" name="name" required autocomplete="name"
                style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; background: var(--color-bg);"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="psych-email" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">Email address *</label>
              <input type="email" id="psych-email" name="email" required autocomplete="email"
                style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; background: var(--color-bg);"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
            <div>
              <label for="ahpra-number" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">AHPRA registration number *</label>
              <input type="text" id="ahpra-number" name="ahpra_number" required placeholder="e.g. PSY0001234567"
                style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; background: var(--color-bg);"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="reg-type" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">Registration type *</label>
              <select id="reg-type" name="registration_type" required
                style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; background: var(--color-bg);"
              >
                <option value="">Select...</option>
                <option value="registered_general">Registered psychologist (general)</option>
                <option value="clinical_endorsed">Clinical psychologist (AHPRA endorsed)</option>
                <option value="registrar">Clinical psychology registrar</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
            <label style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">Specialties (tick all that apply)</label>
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(190px, 1fr)); gap: 0.5rem;">
              {[
                ["spec_gad", "Generalised anxiety (GAD)"],
                ["spec_panic", "Panic disorder"],
                ["spec_social", "Social anxiety"],
                ["spec_health", "Health anxiety"],
                ["spec_ocd", "OCD"],
                ["spec_ptsd", "PTSD / trauma"],
                ["spec_depression", "Depression"],
                ["spec_perinatal", "Perinatal mental health"],
                ["spec_complex", "Complex / comorbid presentations"],
              ].map(([id, label]) => (
                <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); cursor: pointer;">
                  <input type="checkbox" id={id} name={id} value="yes" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;" />
                  {label}
                </label>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
            <div>
              <label for="telehealth" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">Telehealth available? *</label>
              <select id="telehealth" name="telehealth" required
                style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; background: var(--color-bg);"
              >
                <option value="">Select...</option>
                <option value="yes_only">Yes, telehealth only</option>
                <option value="yes_and_in_person">Yes, telehealth and in-person</option>
                <option value="open">Open to telehealth (not currently offering)</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="suburb" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">Practice suburb *</label>
              <input type="text" id="suburb" name="suburb" required placeholder="e.g. Surry Hills, North Sydney"
                style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; background: var(--color-bg);"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
            <label for="description" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">Profile description *</label>
            <p style="font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">This becomes your public listing on the directory. Describe your approach to anxiety, the presentations you work with, your experience, and what a client can expect. Two to four sentences works well.</p>
            <textarea id="description" name="description" rows="5" required placeholder="e.g. I am a registered psychologist with over 8 years of experience helping adults manage generalised anxiety, panic, and social anxiety. I use evidence-based approaches including CBT and ACT, delivered via telehealth across NSW. My focus is on practical, collaborative therapy at a pace that suits you."
              style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; resize: vertical; background: var(--color-bg);"
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
            <label for="booking-url" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">Booking page or practice website URL (optional)</label>
            <input type="url" id="booking-url" name="booking_url" placeholder="https://"
              style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; background: var(--color-bg);"
            />
          </div>

          <div style="margin-bottom: 1.75rem;">
            <label for="notes" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">Anything else you would like us to know (optional)</label>
            <p style="font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Your approach to anxiety, therapy modalities, availability, or any questions about the directory.</p>
            <textarea id="notes" name="notes" rows="4"
              style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; resize: vertical; background: var(--color-bg);"
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <button
            type="submit"
            class="btn btn--primary plausible-event-name=Psych+Form+Submit"
            style="width: 100%; font-size: 1rem; padding: 0.9rem;"
          >
            Apply for a free listing
          </button>

          <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-top: 1rem; text-align: center;">
            Your information is used only to create and manage your directory listing. See our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>

      <hr style="margin: 2.5rem 0;" />

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-top: 0;">Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq">
        <div class="faq__item">
          <p class="faq__q">Is there any cost involved?</p>
          <p class="faq__a">No. Listing your practice is free. There is no subscription fee and no referral fee when a patient enquiry is passed to you. We may introduce a premium tier in future, but founding practitioners will not be charged without explicit notice and consent.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq__item">
          <p class="faq__q">How do you verify AHPRA registration?</p>
          <p class="faq__a">We check the AHPRA Registers of Practitioners before any listing goes live. Expired or lapsed registrations are not listed. If your registration details change, contact us and we will update or remove your listing promptly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq__item">
          <p class="faq__q">Can I update or remove my listing?</p>
          <p class="faq__a">Yes, at any time. Email us from the address associated with your listing and we will make changes or remove your profile within 1 business day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq__item">
          <p class="faq__q">What is a pre-built profile?</p>
          <p class="faq__a">We generate skeleton profiles using only publicly available AHPRA register data (your name, registration type, and principal place of practice suburb). These pages are labelled "Unclaimed" and contain no contact details. Claiming the profile means enriching it with your specialties, booking link, and other details you provide. If you prefer your profile not appear even in unclaimed form, use the form above or email us and we will remove it immediately.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
